item.title: CVE-2023-0149|2024-08-02T05:02:43.734Z -- unknown -- wordprezi
item.description: The WordPrezi WordPress plugin before 0.9 does not validate and escape some of its shortcode attributes before outputting them back in a page/post where the shortcode is embed, which could allow users with the contributor role and above to perform Stored Cross-Site Scripting attacks
